{
  "title": "SFZ Player",
  "children": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "lines": [
        "SFZ sample player",
        "using the sfizz",
        "engine.",
        "",
        "Plays SFZ format",
        "instruments with",
        "full velocity layers,",
        "round robin, and",
        "key switching.",
        "",
        "Upload SFZ instrument",
        "folders to add more",
        "sounds."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Setup",
      "children": [
        {
          "title": "Getting Instruments",
          "lines": [
            "Upload SFZ instrument",
            "folders using the ME",
            "Installer's asset",
            "copy feature.",
            "",
            "Find free instruments:",
            "sfzinstruments.",
            "  github.io",
            "",
            "drolez.com/blog/",
            "  music/ has free",
            "  synth sample packs",
            "",
            "Each instrument is a",
            "folder with .sfz and",
            "WAV files, or a loose",
            ".sfz with samples in",
            "an adjacent folder."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Browsing",
          "lines": [
            "Jog wheel scrolls",
            "through instrument",
            "folders (presets).",
            "",
            "If an instrument has",
            "multiple .sfz files,",
            "use the menu to pick",
            "a variant.",
            "",
            "Last-used variant is",
            "remembered per",
            "instrument."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "File Location",
          "lines": [
            "On-device path:",
            "",
            " instruments/",
            "",
            "Two layouts work:",
            "",
            "1) Folder per instrument:",
            "  MyPiano/",
            "   piano.sfz",
            "   samples/*.wav",
            "",
            "  Multiple .sfz files",
            "  in a folder become",
            "  variants.",
            "",
            "2) Loose .sfz files:",
            "  Be Careful.sfz",
            "  Be Careful Samples/",
            "   *.wav",
            "",
            "  Each .sfz file is",
            "  its own instrument."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Controls",
      "children": [
        {
          "title": "Knobs",
          "lines": [
            "Knob 1: Octave",
            " Transpose -4 to +4",
            " octaves up or down",
            "",
            "Knob 2: Gain",
            " Output level",
            " 0.0 (silent) to",
            " 2.0 (double volume)",
            " Default: 1.0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "MIDI Support",
          "lines": [
            "Notes:",
            " Full velocity",
            " sensitivity with",
            " velocity layers",
            "",
            "Pitch Bend:",
            " Range per SFZ",
            " definition",
            "",
            "Aftertouch:",
            " Channel and poly",
            " aftertouch",
            "",
            "All CCs forwarded",
            "for expression,",
            "sustain pedal, etc.",
            "",
            "Program Change:",
            " Switches instrument",
            " folder"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
